title: Delhi Darbar
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Indian restaurant run by a north Indian guy. More than half the menu is vegetarian but ask about dairy urse. The food is typical Indian. Frequented by westerners, tourists, expats, and Chinese customers. English spoken and has English menu. Near Big Wild Goose Pagoda. Chinese address: 雁塔西路大唐通易坊东头3号
streetAddress: 3 Huan Ta West Road Da Tang Tong Yi Fang
